=head1 DESCRIPTION

This action replaces the email envelope recipients with the given list
of recipients. If the condition of this action applies only to a subset
of recipients, only those recipients are replaced with the recipients
specified in the action. The message contents and headers are
unaffected by this action, only the envelope recipients are updated.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ReplaceWith => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

This action specifies the replacement recipient email addresses to
insert.



